@GuardianService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5272

### Test Moderation (Safe Content)
POST {{GuardianService_HostAddress}}/api/guardian/moderate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Salutare",
  "content": "Acesta este un mesaj de test pentru a verifica moderarea automată."
}

### Test Moderation (Unsafe Content)
POST {{GuardianService_HostAddress}}/api/guardian/moderate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Atac",
  "content": "Vreau să te înjur foarte tare pentru că nu îmi place ce faci."
}

### Test Identity Verification (Moondream)
# Note: You need a base64 string of an image here
POST {{GuardianService_HostAddress}}/api/guardian/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageBase64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mP8z8BQDwAEhQGAhKmMIQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="
}
